my brilliant life ( hangul : 두근두근 내 인생 ; rr : dugeun dugeun nae insaeng ; lit . " my palpitating life " ) is a 2014 south korean drama film starring song hye-kyo and kang dong-won . it was co-written and directed by e j-yong based on the 2011 novel my palpitating life by kim aeran . my brilliant life won the third place audience award at the 17th udine far east film festival in 2015 .